<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Identity — ScholarTrack</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* ── Image Protection for Email Clients ── */
        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border: 0;
            line-height: 100%;
            outline: none;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            padding: 40px 16px;
        }

        .wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* ── Header (Updated to Light Theme) ── */
        .header {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            /* Clean white background */
            border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
            padding: 50px 20px 20px;
            /* Adjusted padding */
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
            /* Very subtle line to separate from content */
        }

        /* Container just for the logo image */
        .logo-container {
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .header-tagline {
            margin-top: 16px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #64748b;
            /* Slate gray text for readability on light bg */
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ── Card ── */
        .card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;
            padding: 40px 40px 36px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            text-align: left;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        }

        .subtext {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #525f7f;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
        }

        /* ── OTP Box ── */
        .otp-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #9ca3af;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .otp-box {
            background: #f8fafc;
            /* Very light slate background */
            border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 32px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 46px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 16px;
            color: #3C3489;
            /* Keeping your brand primary color for the code */
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            text-indent: 16px;
        }

        /* ── Timer ── */
        .timer-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 7px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .timer-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #f59e0b;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* ── Divider ── */
        .divider {
            border: none;
            border-top: 1px solid #eef2f5;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }

        /* ── Warning box ── */
        .warning-box {
            background: #fff7ed;
            border-left: 4px solid #f97316;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .warning-box p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #92400e;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        /* ── Help text ── */
        .help-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            line-height: 1.6;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .help-text a {
            color: #3C3489;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ── Footer ── */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer-divider {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .footer-divider::before,
        .footer-divider::after {
            content: '';
            flex: 1;
            height: 1px;
            background: #e5e7eb;
        }

        .footer-logo {
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #9ca3af;
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
        }

        .footer p {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #b0b7c3;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .footer-links {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="wrapper">

        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo-container">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/3YytxTLh/logo.png" alt="ScholarTrack Logo" width="320"
                    style="display: inline-block; border: none; outline: none; text-decoration: none;" />
            </div>
            <div class="header-tagline">University Scholarship Management Platform</div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">

            <p class="greeting">Hi <%= name %> 👋</p>
            <p class="subtext">
                We received a request to verify your identity on ScholarTrack.
                Use the code below to complete the process.
            </p>

            <div class="otp-label">Your verification code</div>
            <div class="otp-box">
                <div class="otp-code">
                    <%= otp %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timer-row">
                <svg style="width: 18px; height: 18px;" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f59e0b"
                    stroke-width="2">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9" />
                    <path d="M12 7v5l3 3" stroke-linecap="round" />
                </svg>
                <span class="timer-text">This code expires in <strong>2 minutes</strong></span>
            </div>

            <hr class="divider">

            <div class="warning-box">
                <p>
                    <strong>Never share this code.</strong> ScholarTrack will never ask for your
                    verification code via phone, email, or chat. If you did not request this,
                    please <a href="mailto:support@scholartrack.com" style="color:#c2410c;">contact support</a>
                    immediately.
                </p>
            </div>

            <p class="help-text">
                Having trouble? <a href="mailto:support@scholartrack.com">Contact our support team</a>
            </p>

        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-divider">
                <span class="footer-logo">SCHOLAR TRACK</span>
            </div>
            <p>
                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> ScholarTrack. All rights reserved.<br>
                    This is an automated message — please do not reply directly to this email.
            </p>
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
                <a href="#">Terms of Service</a>
                <a href="#">Help Center</a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</body>

</html>